<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="9dafaafc-6398-4a5e-a02f-9c91e2c442e8"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1896717f-3b39-48a2-82c5-42c40df7ae6f">L</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="87fd5440-0154-4a83-85d0-86a3c58072b2">anguages</span>&nbsp;—</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="b67b0e89-aa63-41e0-a757-033cbca399e1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b5d5c443-a69a-4bd4-a31a-c85b329e4302">Challenge</span>&nbsp;0 (10 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="0cdee662-e661-4671-b1e5-6df98d6c11af"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d50254a4-0125-4dbe-b857-c6212a3627cd">Pack Tactics.&nbsp;</span>The baboon has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the baboon’s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn’t <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Incapacitated" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/7-tooltip">incapacitated</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="c2addd4e-5735-4ffb-9e89-2df4587f69c1">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="7ab1231c-675b-4347-b867-058b62c521a8"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="69c3db98-57c0-4d47-97e0-a9cea008d890">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5e5845e4-b48b-4922-b36b-7cc989bf80fb">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+1 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="95e9027e-86ae-4e8d-9756-950a17bd1e38">Hit:&nbsp;</span>1 (1d4 − 1) piercing damage.</p>
