<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="6e1bb273-7392-444c-a6be-261d22a5ce1b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0b19d5f7-a100-4cb9-88f3-3aaa90e3cb9d">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 30 ft., passive Perception 11</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="7ef9efe3-a807-4634-bcdd-f81417a4eac8"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="359fccda-c61b-48d8-b482-abecc68912e8">L</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2627a700-2020-49e2-98df-467d0c421c45">anguages</span>&nbsp;—</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="7525f7d2-a62c-4396-b2c1-29bf68087dab"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5e456f9c-05de-41c5-a229-3af1f4c6e464">Challenge</span>&nbsp;0 (10 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="19696386-33f6-4046-b987-3a1880b3af99"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5fc65612-34c0-4fea-b9de-cc13cca6e4e9">Keen Smell.</span>&nbsp;The badger has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on smell.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="a2fdfb8c-637c-43c7-95b7-8ca19f038f63">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="1fe9099c-4310-4be9-b484-4fe203f03a3a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="888831d0-3264-49e0-b6a7-d2e1df1afbda">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="978ba1cf-3c76-4e2e-b514-0bc138f6d2af">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f04cc48e-1c9b-4770-94a8-212607efe791">Hit:</span>&nbsp;1 piercing damage.</p>
</div>
<div id="_idContainer076" class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="cf147f8b-5ec5-44cf-b091-f74c22dbb467">
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="e9f034ac-0ed4-4c50-891d-97009cbc9be7"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16797-balor" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16797-tooltip">Balor</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="639fcc83-742e-4821-92f9-b4c5eee7cb72">Huge fiend (demon), chaotic evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2e6a8ad7-b471-4d13-a685-57621f0b05a2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="476cfd1b-ed90-4336-9684-85e4880d8770">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;19 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2f739fbb-6fdc-48bc-a9e1-65413794e075"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c98e1b44-5465-455a-bee9-dd52f1f85922">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;262 (21d12 + 126)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="1301480b-1b8f-4407-bf24-53c68a4e6418"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1be1e1d3-4c67-4e05-a4a4-c500cba7b884">Speed</span>&nbsp;40 ft., fly 80 ft.</p>
