<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="5f02946f-ab83-4ea2-a556-b4134288cd17"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e6ed5ed4-5ace-4619-8c80-0a1c88cbc891">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;1 (1d4 − 1)</p>
