<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="bc5d3188-21cd-4109-a740-0b93f22aced1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="29d8e9a6-38c5-4108-af67-bc5432283a2d">Challenge</span>&nbsp;0 (10 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="ca55c49b-78bc-45e3-ad4e-5018ebd85553"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="67ac96c9-c618-4db5-83b2-2bd17a6a5ad1">Echolocation.</span>&nbsp;The bat can’t use its <a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Blindsight" data-tooltip-href="/senses/1-tooltip">blindsight</a> while <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Deafened" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/3-tooltip">deafened</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="fc18c0d0-bd4e-4253-85e0-b40e17895948"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="43dce181-7b43-44b1-b207-4c50d1296e60">Keen Hearing.</span>&nbsp;The bat has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on hearing.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="bf975009-4984-4b32-9adf-7405ec8d5e3c">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="3c1a8908-a2b8-41fd-bcb7-c7f2c1e99db9"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c6bdcc64-1bf1-4aae-877b-a00fe6a7c5a1">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="95eb7d66-554d-488d-8a04-9cae2739e3fa">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+0 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="fe496f34-d781-4a33-9cc6-f494bb3ffa3e">Hit:</span>&nbsp;1 piercing damage.</p>
