<div id="_idContainer265" class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="a2a8bf98-4312-4d99-903a-7577689f77da">
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="1b915a52-eb81-47c4-86a4-388a5aeba8ad"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16803-bearded-devil" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16803-tooltip">Bearded Devil</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="d13c3f07-00ec-4435-ace8-80fe74a8d2db">Medium fiend (devil), lawful evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="a7b7ea8c-6140-45a1-8b9a-c58aad1bbfa2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c14cb944-d4e4-4add-b217-5145a6adc4b5">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;13 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f9b2933d-2fa0-4551-888e-938a35d30722"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4ce826d3-f264-47b7-9bbb-504b2828308d">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;52 (8d8 + 16)</p>
