<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="bc0ba88e-ce59-460e-a711-fd213059f7fe"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="22af55cb-d48c-4bba-93fc-d5a13ff733de">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;19 (3d8 + 6)</p>
