<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="fdd3f6ae-2720-45bb-9d85-885a31e65e08"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f336afb7-7cfa-4cf4-a847-a90a59cdec44">Senses</span>&nbsp;passive Perception 13</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f78879ef-5c11-4dc2-b2ee-b5acf91f46d7"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="76688ddf-01c9-449e-bcc0-2274cfc04889">L</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d256aaba-e0ee-4a03-8e7b-7bed2c1ff2f8">anguages</span>&nbsp;—</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="9ec5a0ac-8dd0-4264-bec2-52d0a5135b71"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b5f84e34-9177-4db2-a46e-bc06443e1c18">Challenge&nbsp;</span>1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="9c508b7b-9b23-4622-ba42-f00c759d61f1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6bab7e18-0c76-4515-91cf-1360e16f298c">Keen Smell.</span>&nbsp;The bear has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on smell.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="30bde05b-00df-495c-8275-f8f9a244791c">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="b7cc3f4a-3a26-4dac-83a1-cf20f7de9285"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="cea2a890-ebbd-4dd0-a75b-488681c5c9f1">Multiattack.</span>&nbsp;The bear makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="dbee5a5c-b382-461e-a0f6-bc4b2addf7d9"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b4b4b31c-09ff-46d7-9d25-2fa987737ff2">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2b63bfe7-e2eb-40ab-86f9-990d72a6e24d">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6f407d1a-9299-425c-822c-ceff919ca50a">Hit:</span>&nbsp;5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="3c7b4ecf-d0aa-4641-84e8-d123897c46db"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1fdae810-b258-47b4-a910-7c5232367f1b">Claws.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="bf88eb97-08a2-4605-bc87-288e9b76b0c4">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="aeef9c6f-f148-46e3-864b-43eaff38f1a8">Hit:</span>&nbsp;7 (2d4 + 2) slashing damage.</p>
