<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="05f9c91c-389c-46cf-b718-66f7eae2130d"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16808-black-pudding" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16808-tooltip">Black Pudding</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="6db3fdff-79bf-4774-98df-1a0abb98ba72">Large ooze, unaligned</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="d4a98910-dc67-4d3f-b345-26f1043c3f6f"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3664cf9e-e81e-4893-b12b-b2c2612494ce">Arm</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="575877b6-97a9-4d29-847e-4d607e656b41">or Class</span>&nbsp;7</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="b44f7381-b1d6-45a8-8781-249f83a632d9"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f9042886-a7c6-4899-af55-27f31ce4114e">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;85 (10d10 + 30)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f654f60a-a4d3-40cf-b3ee-dc0ad79e742b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="060329f8-0f1a-4daa-9d0d-17227c9f0bdc">Speed</span>&nbsp;20 ft., climb 20 ft.</p>
