<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="27a815d0-c789-4f84-b33c-3c68db28f5fe"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e6079207-8b8d-421d-9468-948e796ba614">Sp</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0b13759f-696f-4d3a-86a4-6e6e95a19865">eed</span>&nbsp;40 ft.</p>
