<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="97419b1c-b136-4a18-8f4b-e78106f91efa"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="56766902-a46a-4449-9d12-321214f09e65">Skills</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a> +4, <a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Stealth" data-tooltip-href="/skills/5-tooltip">Stealth</a> +2</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="3efa8bba-8f47-410d-a2e0-1eb25ccac022"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ba762ff7-aefd-468e-a3a9-7d7746f9239b">Damage Immunities</span>&nbsp;lightning</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="96261331-9da3-4fe3-97b9-c56c54649a7b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7f37b041-3f7f-46e9-b634-cd7edaf0d521">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Blindsight" data-tooltip-href="/senses/1-tooltip">blindsight</a> 10 ft., <a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 60 ft., passive Perception 14</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="d6cbb91b-2ef8-4d0a-96de-f821c1e99f7c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1faae4ba-c135-4103-90a0-a4911ecc064e">Language</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2cdc6474-9256-447e-9de1-00fdb3ef057b">s</span>&nbsp;Draconic</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="704b03e9-7723-4e43-812a-238ded86e08e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c16583b3-42a9-49c3-99c2-5143ca83d2e3">Challenge</span>&nbsp;3 (700 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading--after-last-bar-" data-content-chunk-id="b62f513e-eef3-4419-a673-189d55be6166">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="ea12edd8-84c6-4618-872c-907d3f9f47e4"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2410aad3-2857-47eb-a0fd-06cde1adb2ba">Bite.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="40b7f858-26bf-4a3b-a96a-e4ba8b2f089b">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="30bd870c-30b4-4878-9efa-e5fa83525969">Hit:</span>&nbsp;8 (1d10 + 3) piercing damage plus 3 (1d6) lightning damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="2f4a4594-5463-4a3f-9663-5b42ae09a837"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5578d5bb-c669-4c83-91d8-12140166f18d">Lightning Breath (Recharge 5–6).&nbsp;</span>The dragon exhales lightning in a 30-foot line that is 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 22 (4d10) lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>
