<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="5b58d8e2-c48f-4942-bc3c-7bf0034b349a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c403da8d-da4a-45f6-a600-5e6932f80ce8">Challenge&nbsp;</span>1/4 (50 XP)</p>
