<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f48e0f43-5bb4-41ff-8ee7-27b7bba6a2fe"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="9b123db1-1f4d-4fe9-a873-70f842d9eb36">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;16 (3d8 + 3)</p>
